# ZMK build/dev shell (west + Zephyr + gcc-arm-embedded + python) from the
# single root flake. Activates on `cd v1/firmware/zmk`.
#
# The ZMK firmware is built reproducibly with `nix build .#zmk-bundle` from the
# repo ROOT (see ../../../flake.nix -> packages.zmk*). This shell is only for
# manual `west` builds / inspection. `watch_file` reloads the shell when the
# root flake or its lockfile changes.
watch_file ../../../flake.nix ../../../flake.lock
use flake "path:../../..#zmk"
